      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="A No charge order typically refers to a sales order where the customer is not billed for the product or services. This could be due to Various reasons such as promotions, giveaways, warranty replacement etc. It allows to track and process orders without generating revenue invoices i.e., a no-charge order is not posted to accounts receivables"/>
